snippet.title: Shining Stars 2: Mirror Madness RELEASE Trailer
snippet.description:
***UPDATED TO VERSION 1.7***

My second Super Mario 64 hack! Could not be made possible without the help of many others! Special thanks to BroDute for inspiration, Kaze for amazing ASM and custom objects, and my betatesters: mrAgyroth, SuperZora (Asbeth5467), and nathanze1999!

This hack has 122 stars, new music, and improved level design! Collect them all and see what happens when Bowser messes with the great mirror...

All projects (as zip): https://drive.google.com/file/d/1i4q28hpkfH32--YtsE4JX9otwAoJVm-a/view?usp=sharing

Music: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-F3_Cj-fMWw


Tags: Super Mario 64 Shining Stars 2 Mirror Madness Green Star Road Fallen Revenge Luigi Adventure hack awesome new game newer is better bros wii nintendo 64 pieordie1 pieordie 1 sm64ss smwcentral
